

---------------------------
polepos
---------------------------

This project is dependant on the polepos project hosted at SourceFourge:

http://sourceforge.net/projects/polepos
http://www.polepos.org/

The SVN connect string to download polepos is:
https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/polepos


---------------------------
Indianapolis
---------------------------

The Indiananpolis circuit was written to test and document the performance of
the new BTree field index processor.


---------------------------
Some important variables
---------------------------

To see the excellent new results you have to set the following variables correctly:

com.db4o.inside.marshall.MarshallerFamily.VERSION = Version.BTREE_FIELD_INDEXES;

com.db4o.inside.btree.BTree.DEBUG = false;

